unnormalised: mhajjea rogtachea riportant WBC gaṇan 12000/mikrolitar asa dislem, jem daktar Mehrank chintit korunk laglem. koll’llea pormonnem, samanea sima 4500-11000/mikrolitar modli asta, mhonnun tanni infectionakhatir thoddim antibiotics dilim.
normalised: mhajhea rogtachea riportant W-B-C chi sankhya bara hozar prati microliter disli, zaka lagun doctor Mehra chintit zale. Dislem ki samanya seema char hozar panchshe te egar hozar prati microliter asaa, mhunn tannim infection khatir kaim antibiotics dilim.
